<DIV>9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Taunt.&nbsp;&nbsp; Success rate, particularly the steep decline vs. Yellow/Red mobs, is too low and too unreliable, and an "out of range messgae" should not result in a greyed out taunt button.&nbsp;<FONT color=#0000ff>&nbsp; <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></FONT></DIV>
<DIV><BR>10.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Endurance Regen:&nbsp;&nbsp; We need endurance regen from Spells and/or items.&nbsp;&nbsp; Modrods should provide an endurance benefit equal to the mana benefit.&nbsp; Also, change + Endurance only augments to +Endurance regen.&nbsp;<FONT color=#0000ff>&nbsp; <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></FONT></DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:>Ky<FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><FONT color=#000000></FONT></FONT></FONT></P></DIV>
